'''Bioreactors''' were equipment used to power [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Starship/Legends|starships]].<ref name="NJO">''[[The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos I: Hero's Trial]]''</ref>

[[Dark Lord of the Sith/Legends|Dark Lord of the Sith]] [[Darth Plagueis/Legends|Darth Plagueis]] had bioreactors amongst his [[Bacta tank/Legends|bacta tanks]], [[Prison/Legends|cages]], and [[Stasis field/Legends|stasis fields]], all of which were used at his [[Laboratory/Legends|laboratory]] on the island [[Aborah]], at [[Muunilinst/Legends|Muunilinst]]. These devices held life-forms&mdash;many of which came from [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy's]] most remote worlds&mdash;for the [[Sith Lord/Legends|Sith Lord's]] experiments.<ref name="Plagueis">[[Darth Plagueis (novel)|''Darth Plagueis'']]</ref>

